@baseUrl = https://localhost:7006
@token = PASTE_JWT_HERE

### Login (dev admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@sitim.local",
  "password": "Admin12345!"
}

### Who am I
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Local cache list (DB)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/local/studies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sync a study from Orthanc into DB (replace orthancStudyId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/local/studies/{{orthancStudyId}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get study from DB
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/local/studies/{{orthancStudyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sync ALL studies from Orthanc into DB
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/local/studies/sync-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List studies from Orthanc
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/studies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Import DICOM (ZIP)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/studies/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="study.zip"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./path/to/study.zip
------boundary--

### Create analysis job + enqueue (replace orthancStudyId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analyses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orthancStudyId": "{{orthancStudyId}}",
  "modelKey": "demo",
  "forceSyncFromOrthanc": false
}

### Get analysis job (replace analysisId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analyses/{{analysisId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}